This past weekend was Batman Day! (Sep 19th) To celebrate we decided to talk the latest and greatest stories that changed the way we look at Batman today. Whether it be Golden Age, Silver Age, or Modern-day comics, video game franchises, or live-action films, Batman has some of the greatest stories of any comic book character ever. Join us as we gush over some of the best stories ever printed, by some of the heaviest hitters in the comic industry, and try our best to nail what makes Batman so popular! Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media. Send us feedback at ComicBookClique@Gmail.com! You Are Worthy! 

